news.title: Former Trump lawyer Alina Habba is disqualified as top New Jersey prosecutor, US appeals court rules - AP News
news.description: President Donald Trump’s ex-lawyer Alina Habba has been disqualified from serving as New Jersey’s top federal prosecutor. A federal appeals court said Monday the Trump administration’s maneuvers to keep Habba in the role were contrary to federal laws governin…
